      Organise your event
   Large reception room

The history of the château

   The first traces of Château de Saulon go back to the 14^th century; it
   then plays a role of stronghold. During the centuries, the successive
   owners transform the building. The chateau with its current appearance
   originates from the reign of Louis-Philippe (late 18^th-early 19^th
   century).

   In the middle of the 20^th century, the chateau hosts training centres,
   before being transformed into a hotel-restaurant during the years
   1980-90.

   However, it's really in 1997, when Messrs Didier and Lionnel Petitcolas
   acquire the property that Château de Saulon takes off. They revitalise
   the site, carry out major construction works and gradually renovate the
   building, rooms, restaurant, terrace, reception room…

   In 2015, the rooms on the floors are refurbished. Our objective: offer
   you an increasingly satisfying experience.
   The History of the Château
   The chateau and its park

